  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK774">
<l>kaivēl kaḷiṟṟoṭu pōkki varupavaṉ</l>
<l>meyvēl paṟiyā nakum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The hero who after casting the lance in his hand on an elephant, comes (in search of another) will pluck the one (that sticks) in his body and laugh (exultingly).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
